name: Corbett SAndO
overview:
Located, at New Delhi (India), we, “Corbett S And O Equipments Pvt Ltd”, are engaged in trading and supplying high performance range of Echo Smart pen 2GB, Sky Wifi Smart pen 4GB, Sky Wifi Smart pen 8GB Pro, Sky Wifi Smart pen 8GB, Gold Metal Detector, Notebook Accessories, Hand Held Security and Cable and Pipeline.

Our Quality Standards: Adopting international quality standards, we make sure that all the products being traded and supplied by us are according to the client requirements. We are supported by a panel of quality analysts, who stringently inspect each and every product by the help of advance testing machines in order to eliminate any kind of flaws in our product range.

Client Satisfaction: Being a client-concentric organization, we have focused all our activities of meeting the exact needs of our clients’ in the most effectual manner. We have been able to acquire a vast client-base by offering high performance products.

Why Us?: With our vast industry expertise and superior quality products, we have reached the zenith of success and have maintained a remarkable position in the industry. We have carved a niche in the market as a leading trader and supplier of quality assured products.

Vendor Base: In order to achieve complete satisfaction of our customers as well as to meet the international quality standards, we procure our products from the certified vendors of the market. We maintain a healthy relationship with our vendors and they also cooperate with us.
